      "link": "https://en.hespress.com/142399-counterfeit-banknotes-in-morocco-fall-10-in-2025-central-bank-says.html",
      "description": "The number of counterfeit banknotes detected in Morocco fell 10% in both volume and value in 2025 to 4,064 notes, according to Bank Al-Maghrib’s annual report. The central bank attributed the decline to enhanced security features on Moroccan banknotes, upgraded counterfeit detection equipment and expanded inspections of banks and private cash-sorting centres. Bank Al-Maghrib said […] The post Counterfeit banknotes in Morocco fall 10% in 2025, central bank says appeared first on HESPRESS English ",
